channel.description: Recent content in Bishop|Inyo County|California|United States on Roadsign Pictures

item.title: US-395 North at US-6
item.description: US-395 north at US-6 in Bishop. Use US-6 east for Tonopah (Nevada). This is the western terminus of US-6. The eastern end of US-6 is Provincetown, MA.

item.title: US-395 North Approaching US-6
item.description: US-395 north approaching US-6 in Bishop. Use US-6 east for US-95. This is the western terminus of US-6.

item.title: US-395 South/CA-168 East - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance marker on US-395 South/CA-168 East. Distance to Big Pine, Independence, and Los Angeles.

item.title: US-395 South at CA-168 West
item.description: US-395 South at CA-168 West to Lake Sabrina and South Lake. CA-168 east joins US-395 south to Big Pine.

item.title: End US-6 West at US-395
item.description: End US-6 west at US-395. Use US-395 north for Reno (Nevada); US-395 south for Los Angeles. US-6 begins in Provincetown, Massachusetts.

item.title: US-6 West Approaching US-395
item.description: Approaching western end of US-6 at US-395 junction. Turn right for US-395 north towards Reno (Nevada). Continue ahead for US-395 south towards Los Angeles.
